00:00:04.320 --> 00:00:05.030
Law...

3
00:00:05.780 --> 00:00:06.570
Law...

4
00:00:08.820 --> 00:00:09.660
Go...

5
00:00:10.450 --> 00:00:11.240
Law...

6
00:00:17.540 --> 00:00:19.920
<b>2nd

Basement

Floor</b>

7
00:00:26.050 --> 00:00:28.130
My real name is...

8
00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:31.970
Trafalgar D. Water Law.

9
00:00:34.560 --> 00:00:35.810
Is that a secret?

10
00:00:36.980 --> 00:00:37.850
Yes.

11
00:00:38.480 --> 00:00:41.940
I'm surprised. So you have
a D. in your name, too.

12
00:00:42.480 --> 00:00:44.400
I'm telling you because I trust you.

13
00:00:45.150 --> 00:00:46.110
Thank you.

14
00:00:46.650 --> 00:00:49.820
But... I don't have any answers for you.

15
00:00:50.780 --> 00:00:52.570
Luffy might not care,

16
00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:54.240
but personally...

17
00:00:54.780 --> 00:00:57.290
I want to learn the meaning of D., too.

18
00:00:58.960 --> 00:01:01.250
So all we can do is follow the red stones?

19
00:01:02.460 --> 00:01:03.960
Indeed...

20
00:01:04.340 --> 00:01:07.300
And that means toppling the Four Emperors.

21
00:01:08.210 --> 00:01:11.680
It's not as if they'll just
hand them over, after all.

22
00:01:13.090 --> 00:01:14.760
This isn't it...

23
00:01:15.510 --> 00:01:17.350
It needs to be red.

24
00:01:17.350 --> 00:01:20.270
In some places, the people
of the D. have been called...

25
00:01:21.520 --> 00:01:23.190
"the Natural Enemies of the Gods!"

26
00:01:33.410 --> 00:01:35.620
Hey, Cora...

27
00:01:36.620 --> 00:01:38.290
I still wanna know...

28
00:01:39.500 --> 00:01:41.620
why I have to lead...

29
00:01:42.620 --> 00:01:44.250
such a checkered life.

30
00:01:49.170 --> 00:01:52.040
Open up the borderless map, then

31
00:01:52.040 --> 00:01:55.240
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

32
00:01:55.240 --> 00:01:59.630
LET’S SAIL ON right now, hoist your sails up high

33
00:01:59.630 --> 00:02:02.620
Riding on the wind

34
00:02:07.750 --> 00:02:11.960
DON’T GIVE UP, it’s time to finish what we started

35
00:02:12.150 --> 00:02:14.930
So don't you grow disheartened

36
00:02:15.240 --> 00:02:18.690
Laugh the tears away through the storm

37
00:02:18.890 --> 00:02:23.120
SHOUT IT OUT, when you feel down always remember

38
00:02:23.460 --> 00:02:25.720
That’s what your friends are there for

39
00:02:25.750 --> 00:02:27.880
Y’know there’s no point in fronting,

40
00:02:27.880 --> 00:02:31.800
your crew will always have your back

41
00:02:32.170 --> 00:02:35.900
Even in the face of utter darkness

42
00:02:36.130 --> 00:02:38.890
C’mon, BRAVE IT OUT We’ll be alright

43
00:02:39.190 --> 00:02:42.680
Together you know that we’ll never lose a fight

44
00:02:42.900 --> 00:02:45.670
Open up the borderless map, then

45
00:02:45.690 --> 00:02:48.530
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

46
00:02:48.830 --> 00:02:53.110
All great journeys starts with a single step

47
00:02:53.180 --> 00:02:54.120
DREAMIN’ ON

48
00:02:54.120 --> 00:02:56.900
Open up the borderless map, then

49
00:02:56.900 --> 00:02:59.640
Raise the flag we swore to defend

50
00:02:59.790 --> 00:03:02.530
We’ll never stop until we’ve reached the top

51
00:03:02.600 --> 00:03:07.000
Just be true to yourself until the end

52
00:03:07.130 --> 00:03:11.840
Set sail and grab it, DREAMIN ON

53
00:03:22.310 --> 00:03:24.180
Usopp! Are you okay?!

54
00:03:25.940 --> 00:03:28.560
Who d'ya think I am?!

55
00:03:28.560 --> 00:03:30.400
I'm most certainly not okay...

56
00:03:31.230 --> 00:03:34.030
No, you most certainly aren't...

57
00:03:35.070 --> 00:03:37.910
But at the very least, I am.

58
00:03:37.910 --> 00:03:38.570
Seriously?

59
00:03:38.610 --> 00:03:41.370
<b>Flame Clouds</b>

60
00:03:41.700 --> 00:03:44.790
Hey, Otama. How did you get here?

61
00:03:44.790 --> 00:03:47.500
One of the enemies gave me a boat ride!

62
00:03:47.500 --> 00:03:49.380
What?! An enemy?!

63
00:03:50.840 --> 00:03:53.340
Pay-Pay! Chew that dog up!

64
00:03:53.670 --> 00:03:55.670
Do it yourself!

65
00:04:03.890 --> 00:04:06.520
Damn! What's with this baboon?!

66
00:04:06.520 --> 00:04:09.600
Wherever did he come from?!

67
00:04:09.600 --> 00:04:10.770
Hihimaru!

68
00:04:10.770 --> 00:04:13.070
Keep them busy for three minutes!

69
00:04:15.780 --> 00:04:19.490
Those two mean business!
That giant monkey will get hurt!

70
00:04:20.740 --> 00:04:23.870
Don't underestimate us, Onami!

71
00:04:24.490 --> 00:04:26.160
We came here...

72
00:04:26.540 --> 00:04:28.460
as samurai!

73
00:04:35.000 --> 00:04:37.380
Get out of my way!

74
00:05:03.490 --> 00:05:06.830
We can do this forever, Young Master Yamato.

75
00:05:07.330 --> 00:05:13.040
Although, I can't go losing any more
of my impregnable Armored Division.

76
00:05:13.790 --> 00:05:16.050
How dare you harm so many of them?!

77
00:05:16.460 --> 00:05:17.420
Aim!

78
00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:25.350
Fire!

79
00:05:29.640 --> 00:05:32.060
Momonosuke! Shinobu!

80
00:05:50.910 --> 00:05:52.540
Yamato...

81
00:05:52.540 --> 00:05:55.000
If you keep taking bullets...

82
00:05:55.670 --> 00:05:57.130
This is nothing.

83
00:06:03.220 --> 00:06:06.510
If you are a samurai, then you must decide!

84
00:06:07.010 --> 00:06:10.180
Leave me here and take Lord Momonosuke...

85
00:06:10.180 --> 00:06:10.930
No!

86
00:06:14.270 --> 00:06:15.560
If it were Oden...

87
00:06:18.770 --> 00:06:21.110
If it were Kozuki Oden...

88
00:06:21.780 --> 00:06:24.780
he would never do that!

89
00:06:37.710 --> 00:06:39.300
How stubborn...

90
00:06:43.340 --> 00:06:48.220
Do you really think you can defeat me
while you're fretting over those weaklings?

91
00:06:48.800 --> 00:06:52.020
What arrogance, Young Master Yamato!

92
00:06:52.020 --> 00:06:53.520
Sasaki...

93
00:07:23.630 --> 00:07:24.720
What just happened?!

94
00:07:27.590 --> 00:07:30.180
Outta my way! Outta my way!

95
00:07:30.180 --> 00:07:33.180
Get outta my way!

96
00:07:35.690 --> 00:07:37.020
Franosuke!

97
00:07:38.350 --> 00:07:39.940
Huh? Momo?!

98
00:07:40.400 --> 00:07:43.990
Good to see you alive and kicking!
Shinobu, you doing okay there?!

99
00:07:44.650 --> 00:07:45.900
That's...

100
00:07:49.200 --> 00:07:51.870
I know him! He's part of Luffy's crew!

101
00:07:52.410 --> 00:07:56.580
Cyborg Franky! He's worth 94 million berries!

102
00:08:01.210 --> 00:08:03.880
It's hard to believe he's real!

103
00:08:14.520 --> 00:08:16.980
Haccha?! Why are you here?!

104
00:08:19.310 --> 00:08:21.020
Oh no, not good!

105
00:08:23.940 --> 00:08:25.820
Don't you dare, dumbass!

106
00:08:25.820 --> 00:08:29.030
Is this because you couldn't
catch me?! How childish!

107
00:08:43.090 --> 00:08:47.630
Armored Division! Don't lose them!
Keep them from running at any cost!

108
00:09:00.390 --> 00:09:02.440
He broke the floor!

109
00:09:02.440 --> 00:09:04.270
Oh, right! There's a floor beneath us!

110
00:09:04.730 --> 00:09:08.440
Momonosuke! Shinobu!
Let's make our way down like this!

111
00:09:08.740 --> 00:09:11.450
Momo! Shinobu! Are you okay?!

112
00:09:11.450 --> 00:09:12.950
Did you get caught?!

113
00:09:12.950 --> 00:09:16.040
No! This is an ally!

114
00:09:18.120 --> 00:09:21.460
Cyborg Franky! I'll leave the enemy to you!

115
00:09:21.790 --> 00:09:22.920
Who are you?!

116
00:09:22.920 --> 00:09:26.210
Luffy entrusted these two to me!

117
00:09:26.750 --> 00:09:29.340
I don't know who you are...

118
00:09:29.340 --> 00:09:33.340
but I got it! You can super count on me!

119
00:09:35.010 --> 00:09:37.600
Shinobu, take Momonosuke!

120
00:09:37.600 --> 00:09:38.180
What?

121
00:09:39.060 --> 00:09:40.520
I wanna return a favor!

122
00:09:41.060 --> 00:09:42.060
I'll be right back!

123
00:09:42.350 --> 00:09:44.150
I gotta take him down at least...

124
00:09:48.570 --> 00:09:50.570
Narikabura Arrow!

125
00:10:04.830 --> 00:10:04.870
<b>Narikabura</b>

126
