<b>Arrow</b>
<b>Narikabura</b>

140
00:10:05.450 --> 00:10:05.500
<b>Arrow</b>
<b>Narikabura</b>

141
00:10:05.500 --> 00:10:05.540
<b>Arrow</b>
<b>Narikabura</b>

142
00:10:05.540 --> 00:10:05.580
<b>Arrow</b>
<b>Narikabura</b>

143
00:10:05.580 --> 00:10:05.620
<b>Arrow</b>
<b>Narikabura</b>

144
00:10:05.620 --> 00:10:08.170
<b>Narikabura</b>
<b>Arrow</b>

145
00:10:14.970 --> 00:10:16.430
Alright!

146
00:10:26.900 --> 00:10:28.570
That stranger did this?!

147
00:10:31.490 --> 00:10:33.360
Who was that?

148
00:10:33.860 --> 00:10:35.240
Haccha?!

149
00:10:35.240 --> 00:10:36.030
Dammit!

150
00:10:36.570 --> 00:10:40.450
Yamato took Momonosuke down that hole!

151
00:10:40.450 --> 00:10:43.580
Organize a pursuit unit! Chase after them now!

152
00:10:44.170 --> 00:10:47.540
Armored Division!
Let's deal with the damn robot!

153
00:11:06.150 --> 00:11:07.400
Momonosuke!

154
00:11:08.230 --> 00:11:09.770
You must survive!

155
00:11:11.570 --> 00:11:13.610
Survive at any cost!

156
00:11:14.200 --> 00:11:16.950
The one who'll lead the world to a new dawn...

157
00:11:17.360 --> 00:11:18.780
is you!

158
00:11:23.450 --> 00:11:25.460
Kaido!

159
00:11:25.460 --> 00:11:27.670
How annoying!

160
00:11:53.110 --> 00:11:58.320
You've already lost, you fools!

161
00:12:20.930 --> 00:12:21.680
She's coming!

162
00:12:27.350 --> 00:12:29.440
Big Mom is back!

163
00:12:37.110 --> 00:12:40.660
Don't worry! I'm only interested in going...

164
00:12:41.030 --> 00:12:43.780
up to where Kaido is.

165
00:13:05.970 --> 00:13:09.270
I know how to fight the virus!

166
00:13:09.270 --> 00:13:10.770
You do?!

167
00:13:20.070 --> 00:13:21.700
Run, Apoo!

168
00:13:22.110 --> 00:13:26.290
You'd better not let this show end just yet!

169
00:13:29.540 --> 00:13:30.500
Omasa!

170
00:13:31.330 --> 00:13:33.250
Hey! Come to your senses!

171
00:13:34.420 --> 00:13:36.250
There's no other option, huh?

172
00:13:39.380 --> 00:13:43.840
No... I've finally made it this far...

173
00:13:43.840 --> 00:13:46.810
I don't want to die here!

174
00:13:46.810 --> 00:13:48.430
Please, help me...

175
00:14:31.060 --> 00:14:33.310
He's still on my tail!

176
00:14:34.140 --> 00:14:37.310
What a pain! He won't give it a rest!

177
00:14:37.860 --> 00:14:39.070
Apoo!

178
00:14:41.150 --> 00:14:43.150
Give me the antibody!

179
00:14:43.150 --> 00:14:44.990
Drake, you bastard!

180
00:14:48.910 --> 00:14:50.830
You're here! Back me up!

181
00:14:57.710 --> 00:15:01.000
What are you doing?!
We gotta fight him together!

182
00:15:07.760 --> 00:15:08.430
Damn you!

183
00:15:09.850 --> 00:15:12.770
Like I said, it isn't fair to fight me as a duet!

184
00:15:12.770 --> 00:15:15.810
He wants a solo against me!

185
00:15:15.810 --> 00:15:17.400
Isn't that right?!

186
00:15:23.440 --> 00:15:27.780
Beats me what's going on here.
I didn't expect you to be so chill with it!

187
00:15:27.780 --> 00:15:30.580
Alright, then... Check it out!

188
00:15:33.120 --> 00:15:33.870
What?!

189
00:16:00.560 --> 00:16:02.070
Hey! Zoro!

190
00:16:03.690 --> 00:16:05.150
Oh, Chopper.

191
00:16:06.360 --> 00:16:07.570
Thanks!

192
00:16:07.570 --> 00:16:10.120
Can I leave this floor to you?

193
00:16:10.740 --> 00:16:12.780
I can't stay for the show.

194
00:16:13.290 --> 00:16:15.040
You'll live, right?

195
00:16:15.500 --> 00:16:16.410
Of course!

196
00:16:16.750 --> 00:16:19.630
I've already figured out how the virus works!

197
00:16:20.880 --> 00:16:22.380
That's my guy!

198
00:16:22.420 --> 00:16:26.220
<b>Third Floor</b>

199
00:16:50.110 --> 00:16:52.950
Is he gonna gather all the metal in the castle?!

200
00:16:52.950 --> 00:16:53.660
Dammit!

201
00:16:56.120 --> 00:16:58.370
Eustass Captain Kid!

202
00:17:00.170 --> 00:17:03.250
Stop him! Don't let him get to the rooftop!

203
00:17:04.130 --> 00:17:05.550
They're coming.

204
00:17:06.000 --> 00:17:08.050
Let me greet them...

205
00:17:08.420 --> 00:17:11.840
with this overwhelming amount of mass!

206
00:17:20.890 --> 00:17:25.400
It's fine if you don't move outta
the way. Just come right to us!

207
00:17:34.240 --> 00:17:36.790
Do you think this is enough, Killer?!

208
00:17:39.960 --> 00:17:43.290
Our enemy is the world's strongest pirate...

209
00:17:43.290 --> 00:17:46.000
You can never have too much.

210
00:17:48.130 --> 00:17:49.420
You said it!

211
00:17:57.560 --> 00:17:59.140
Stop Straw Hat!

212
00:18:05.940 --> 00:18:07.520
What floor are we on?!

213
00:18:07.520 --> 00:18:09.860
We're coming up on the third floor!

214
00:18:09.860 --> 00:18:12.400
The rooftop is above the fifth floor!

215
00:18:12.780 --> 00:18:15.410
Alright! Kin'emon, wait for me!

216
00:18:17.580 --> 00:18:18.290
That's...

217
00:18:18.660 --> 00:18:20.870
Hey! Do you guys hear that?

218
00:18:20.870 --> 00:18:22.410
Huh? Hear what?

219
00:18:22.750 --> 00:18:26.040
Oh no... It's coming from the third floor!

220
00:18:27.000 --> 00:18:30.260
Whaddya say? Whaddya say?

221
00:18:30.260 --> 00:18:31.590
Please don't!

222
00:18:37.760 --> 00:18:39.560
I need it!

223
00:18:40.560 --> 00:18:41.770
You ought not!

224
00:18:41.770 --> 00:18:43.190
How naughty!

225
00:18:51.990 --> 00:18:54.450
Wait for us, Kin'emon!

226
00:18:57.780 --> 00:18:59.120
Which way is the rooftop?!

227
00:19:00.330 --> 00:19:01.330
That way!

228
00:19:01.330 --> 00:19:02.370
Alright!

229
00:19:08.340 --> 00:19:11.460
Whaddya say? Whaddya say?

230
00:19:11.460 --> 00:19:14.340
You ought not! You ought not!

231
00:19:14.340 --> 00:19:16.340
How naughty!

232
00:19:17.640 --> 00:19:19.640
I have something serious to attend to.

233
00:19:19.640 --> 00:19:21.720
You guys, go ahead!

234
00:19:22.100 --> 00:19:24.480
I'll catch up as soon as I'm done!

235
00:19:28.190 --> 00:19:29.270
I hear it!

236
00:19:29.270 --> 00:19:31.610
How naughty!

237
00:19:31.610 --> 00:19:32.940
A beautiful woman...

238
00:19:32.940 --> 00:19:34.320
is calling for help!

239
00:19:36.740 --> 00:19:39.410
How naughty!

240
00:19:40.030 --> 00:19:41.870
That's it, come here!

241
00:19:41.870 --> 00:19:45.160
Oh, you ought not do this!

242
00:19:48.710 --> 00:19:52.380
You're a real cutie, so whaddya say?

243
00:19:52.380 --> 00:19:53.590
You ought not!

244
00:19:55.550 --> 00:19:57.130
Whaddya say?

245
00:19:57.130 --> 00:19:58.720
You really ought not!

246
00:19:59.970 --> 00:20:01.720
Whaddya say?

247
00:20:01.720 --> 00:20:03.430
Please stop!

248
00:20:03.430 --> 00:20:07.810
How naughty!

249
00:20:08.020 --> 00:20:10.400
Samurai-style sexual harassment!

250
00:20:10.400 --> 00:20:13.020
"Whaddya say?", "How naughty!"

251
00:20:13.020 --> 00:20:15.860
How naughty!

252
00:20:16.610 --> 00:20:21.370
Someone in a position of power is
untying a helpless woman's kimono.

253
00:20:21.370 --> 00:20:25.660
What the spinning woman
loses with each turn...

254
00:20:26.250 --> 00:20:27.660
isn't just her dress!

255
00:20:28.540 --> 00:20:29.420
It's her dignity!

256
00:20:34.300 --> 00:20:36.510
Just hold on! Help is on the way!

257
00:20:36.510 --> 00:20:37.590
Whaddya...?

258
00:20:37.590 --> 00:20:39.220
It's not right!

259
00:20:39.720 --> 00:20:41.180
Stop it!

260
00:20:45.770 --> 00:20:47.770
What?! What's this?!

261
00:20:47.770 --> 00:20:50.940
How naughty!

262
00:20:52.980 --> 00:20:54.150
A spider web?!

263
00:20:54.150 --> 00:20:57.070
How naughty!

264
00:20:57.400 --> 00:20:58.650
Hey, stop that!

265
00:20:58.650 --> 00:21:01.530
How naughty!

266
00:21:06.160 --> 00:21:07.540
– Naughty Trap!
– Naughty Trap!

267
00:21:24.350 --> 00:21:28.350
Another perv in shining armor came...

268
00:21:28.350 --> 00:21:30.350
Damn... It was a trap...

269
00:21:30.980 --> 00:21:34.820
Black Leg Sanji of the Straw Hat Pirates.

270
00:21:35.190 --> 00:21:38.070
He's worth 330 million berries!

271
00:21:38.070 --> 00:21:40.860
Probably competing with his crewmate Zoro.

272
00:21:40.860 --> 00:21:43.820
I think this one's bounty is higher.

273
00:21:43.820 --> 00:21:45.950
Wow! We caught some big game!

274
00:21:48.080 --> 00:21:51.330
Untie me now and I'll let this slide!

275
00:21:51.330 --> 00:21:54.540
Oh, how scary! You're blackmailing us!

276
00:21:54.540 --> 00:21:56.670
I have somewhere to be!

277
00:21:57.170 --> 00:22:00.720
If you go, the battlefield will just spill over.

278
00:22:01.680 --> 00:22:06.260
And I don't want this banquet
hall to be caught up in it.

279
00:22:06.890 --> 00:22:10.850
My allies are waiting for me!
Untie the damn rope already!

280
00:22:11.980 --> 00:22:16.820
Boys with dirty mouths get me all tingly.

281
00:22:16.820 --> 00:22:19.690
"Boy"?! Stop messing with me!

282
00:22:20.440 --> 00:22:24.360
Hey... what do you say?

283
00:22:25.570 --> 00:22:27.240
Do you...

284
00:22:28.080 --> 00:22:29.200
like me?

285
00:22:29.200 --> 00:22:32.040
Cut it out! I don't...

286
00:22:33.540 --> 00:22:35.170
I don't like you...

287
00:22:38.550 --> 00:22:40.260
I love you!

288
00:22:42.220 --> 00:22:45.050
<b>Elsewhere,

on the Third Floor...</b>

289
00:22:45.050 --> 00:22:49.010
Hey, Gorishiro! You're getting banana on me!

290
00:22:48.430 --> 00:22:53.850
<b>Mizerka
Beast Pirates Headliner
Gorilla Smile Fruit</b>

291
00:22:50.180 --> 00:22:53.850
Master Poker! Straw Hat and Jinbe
are heading your way!

292
00:22:54.810 --> 00:22:56.610
Yeah, got it.

293
00:22:55.600 --> 00:23:00.150
<b>Poker
Beast Pirates Headliner
Rattlesnake Smile Fruit</b>

294
00:22:56.610 --> 00:22:59.270
Regrettably, I let Kid through...

295
00:23:02.110 --> 00:23:05.160
But look! Straw Hat's bounty
is 1.5 billion berries!

296
00:23:05.160 --> 00:23:08.740
Taking him down will do more
than just clear my name!

297
00:23:10.290 --> 00:23:12.370
Aw, man! Come on!

298
00:23:13.330 --> 00:23:16.710
Me, in the Soaring Six? That'll do nicely.

299
00:23:17.250 --> 00:23:19.090
Straw Hat! Straw Hat!

300
00:23:19.670 --> 00:23:20.550
This way!

301
00:23:20.880 --> 00:23:22.380
Who are they?

302
00:23:22.380 --> 00:23:24.050
Oh, it's you guys!

303
00:23:24.050 --> 00:23:25.970
The ones from Udon!

304
00:23:27.640 --> 00:23:29.850
Hey, Straw Hat isn't here yet?!

305
00:23:30.510 --> 00:23:32.600
He should be there soon!

306
00:23:36.600 --> 00:23:37.850
A ladder...

307
00:23:37.850 --> 00:23:40.650
Yeah, you can climb
to the fourth floor with this.

308
00:23:40.650 --> 00:23:43.360
A bunch of enemies are waiting at the stairs.

309
00:23:43.360 --> 00:23:45.740
That helps a lot. Thanks!

310
00:23:51.410 --> 00:23:53.450
Where is he?!

311
00:23:57.710 --> 00:23:59.790
Everyone, listen up!

312
00:23:59.790 --> 00:24:02.460
Use fire against the ice ogres!

313
00:24:02.460 --> 00:24:07.010
This virus fuses with
the gas that's chilling our bodies!

314
00:24:07.010 --> 00:24:08.840
Look at me!

315
00:24:08.840 --> 00:24:12.720
If you stop the chill, the virus can't multiply!

316
00:24:17.230 --> 00:24:20.690
Meanwhile, I'll make enough
antibodies for everyone!

317
00:24:23.650 --> 00:24:28.110
I'm a doctor! I'll save everyone,
both allies and enemies!

318
00:24:29.490 --> 00:24:30.450
– What?!
– What?!

319
00:24:30.450 --> 00:24:33.330
Everyone?! Including Omasa?!

320
00:24:35.660 --> 00:24:40.250
So stay alive! Don't let
that horrible man kill you!

321
00:24:44.420 --> 00:24:47.670
How nice, tanuki!

322
00:24:48.880 --> 00:24:52.050
And you're pathetic, Apoo!

323
00:24:52.050 --> 00:24:55.180
I presented you with such
a fun little ogre game...

324
00:24:55.180 --> 00:24:58.770
and you just had to go and ruin it!

325
00:24:59.440 --> 00:25:02.270
You two have gotten on my last nerve!

326
00:25:08.110 --> 00:25:08.860
What?!

327
00:25:10.820 --> 00:25:12.570
Screw the game!

328
00:25:12.570 --> 00:25:13.450
What?

329
00:25:13.450 --> 00:25:19.870
I didn't come to this island
to play around with you losers!

330
00:25:19.870 --> 00:25:22.540
I came to chop up Kaido...

331
00:25:22.540 --> 00:25:25.710
the so-called strongest man in the world!

332
00:25:32.640 --> 00:25:33.470
What?!

333
00:25:33.470 --> 00:25:36.390
His anger triggered an earthquake?!

334
00:25:36.390 --> 00:25:38.810
Was that conqueror's haki?!

335
00:25:47.730 --> 00:25:50.650
Hold on to something!
Everyone, hang in there!

336
00:25:53.490 --> 00:25:57.620
Zoro, what did you do?!
I can't believe you did this!

337
00:25:57.620 --> 00:25:59.290
There's no way that was me.

338
00:26:04.460 --> 00:26:06.590
What's with this shaking?!

339
00:26:06.590 --> 00:26:08.000
I'm scared!

340
00:26:08.840 --> 00:26:11.220
No, I'm not scared!

341
00:26:11.760 --> 00:26:14.430
You'll be fine! Just keep moving forward!

342
00:26:14.430 --> 00:26:16.010
Let's hurry up!

343
00:26:24.190 --> 00:26:26.940
What's this?! Is it an earthquake, Jinbe?!

344
00:26:26.940 --> 00:26:30.150
Geologically speaking,
this island is unique, but...

345
00:26:46.000 --> 00:26:48.500
It's no use! We can't reach the shore!

346
00:26:48.500 --> 00:26:51.210
Let's pull away from Onigashima for now!

347
00:27:03.140 --> 00:27:04.100
What the...

348
00:27:06.100 --> 00:27:08.060
How impatient...

349
00:27:13.900 --> 00:27:15.860
Is the island sinking?!

350
00:27:37.390 --> 00:27:41.100
Onigashima's... What the hell is going on?!

351
00:27:41.100 --> 00:27:44.730
Do you think the captain is okay?!

352
00:27:49.690 --> 00:27:54.490
<b>Port Area,

Outside the Dome</b>

353
00:27:55.950 --> 00:27:59.070
Momonosuke! Your survival
is the highest priority!

354
00:27:59.070 --> 00:28:01.120
Let's board a ship and get out of here!

355
00:28:01.950 --> 00:28:03.330
We've gotta hurry.

356
00:28:04.580 --> 00:28:06.330
I have a bad feeling about this!

357
00:28:14.260 --> 00:28:15.550
What was that?

358
00:28:16.220 --> 00:28:18.050
It stopped shaking.

359
00:28:23.930 --> 00:28:27.060
I know how you feel, Zoro... I saw it, too.

360
00:28:27.560 --> 00:28:29.940
Okiku's arm!

361
00:28:33.820 --> 00:28:35.940
Me as well!

362
00:28:36.820 --> 00:28:38.820
I'm late to the party.

363
00:28:38.820 --> 00:28:41.240
I wish I could just fly there.

364
00:28:41.780 --> 00:28:44.950
But every route has its challenges.

365
00:29:02.470 --> 00:29:04.060
Straw Hats!

366
00:29:04.060 --> 00:29:05.680
Marco the Phoenix!

367
00:29:05.680 --> 00:29:07.390
Yep, the one and only!

368
00:29:07.730 --> 00:29:11.520
You guys are the VIPs!
Why are you still slumming it down here?

369
00:29:12.150 --> 00:29:14.610
It's not like we want to be.

370
00:29:15.280 --> 00:29:17.860
Is there anything I can do to help?

371
00:29:28.040 --> 00:29:31.620
The Beast Pirates' ships... They're gone!

372
00:29:31.620 --> 00:29:32.580
What?!

373
00:29:48.020 --> 00:29:49.230
So is the sea!

374
00:29:49.230 --> 00:29:51.890
What?! What do you mean by that?!

375
00:29:52.900 --> 00:29:54.360
It's too late!

376
00:29:55.860 --> 00:29:58.320
We can no longer flee to the sea!

377
00:29:58.780 --> 00:30:01.070
Is this not a port?!

378
00:30:02.070 --> 00:30:03.570
That quake before...

379
00:30:05.700 --> 00:30:07.120
I get it now!

380
00:30:07.450 --> 00:30:10.290
What is going on, Yamato?!

381
00:30:15.250 --> 00:30:19.760
Dragons fly through the air
by creating flame clouds!

382
00:30:24.340 --> 00:30:25.800
That means that right now...

383
00:30:37.650 --> 00:30:40.900
Kaido is making Onigashima fly!

384
00:30:44.910 --> 00:30:49.040
He's gonna relocate
the island to the Flower Capital!

385
00:30:55.040 --> 00:30:57.040
N-No way...

386
00:31:36.210 --> 00:31:38.580
Are you satisfied now?

387
00:31:38.580 --> 00:31:40.710
The Kozuki are finished.

388
00:31:41.670 --> 00:31:45.170
Wano, or more accurately, New Onigashima,

389
00:31:45.170 --> 00:31:48.680
will become a stronghold for pirates.

390
00:32:00.520 --> 00:32:04.990
Let's usher in a world of violence!
